      "text": [
        " السَّرْجُ مَرْكَبٌ مَلْعُونٌ لِلنِّسَاءِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from one of his companions, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The saddle riding is detestable for the women’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from certain persons of his people who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The saddle is a condemned riding thing for women.”’ "
        ]
